vagrant: making boxen to make it available for others to download and use
vagrant-sahara: a plugin to vagrant to give you snapshots to use as sandboxes
foreman: a way to abstract away upstart or init scripts, and make using multiprocess apps easier to work with

Also this: http://wiki.opscode.com/display/chef/Installing+Chef+Server+Manually#InstallingChefServerManually-ConfiguretheCommandLineClient for post-install
